  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nMy Text size setting in the Appearance is set to XXL, but when I open the app after a restart, the text size shown is clearly M. \r\n\r\nAfter restart:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11926403/204041396-15d30361-36d7-4424-93e7-44b0c5b512d9.png)\r\n\r\nWhat it should look like:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11926403/204041434-0755949e-b6a6-4502-8147-152f98e18c3b.png)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Set text size to XXL\r\n2. Close the app\r\n3. Reopen\r\n4. Text seems small again (but the setting still says XXL) \r\n\r\nOnly way to get it back to XXL is to change it to something else and back to XXL\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Master (`c1fd4cc6809c88f138a1ff661b7291967456e05b`)\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu 20\r\n\r\n",
